r-base loop was\nblown out by the loop's twist from the reconnection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Apr 2016 22:52:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 May 2016 23:36:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-25"}
