ude multiple kinds of data in the comparison,\nsuggesting that the ID metric is appropriate for use in a calibration of the\nKPP model parameters using mooring observations of the ocean state.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Apr 2016 03:28:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-21"}
