 the Eddington ratio and is correlated with the black hole mass.\nThe reliability of these results is fortified with Monte Carlo simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Apr 2016 08:49:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Jul 2016 17:21:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 3 Mar 2017 09:22:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-06"}
