. As a result of new factorizations of the law of the exponential\nfunctional we deliver important intertwining relation between members of the\nclass of positive self-similar semigroups.\n  The derivation of our results relies on a mixture of complex-analytical and\nprobabilistic techniques.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Apr 2016 13:53:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 3 Sep 2016 15:03:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 28 Oct 2017 14:58:02 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 23 Jul 2018 09:01:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-24"}
